{"lastModified":1771255874407,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEmbark on a Seafaring Odyssey:\n\nStep into the world of “Lella Belle,” an Oceanis 46.1 masterpiece designed to redefine your sailing experience. Crafted in 2024, this vessel seamlessly blends contemporary luxury with cutting-edge features, inviting you to embark on a journey where comfort and sophistication meet the open sea.\n\nDiscover the Essence of “Lella Belle”:\n\n• Timeless Elegance: “Lella Belle” boasts a design that marries modern aesthetics with classic charm, creating an atmosphere of unparalleled beauty on the open waters.\n• 2024 Construction: Setting sail into the future, “Lella Belle” is a product of the latest advancements in yacht construction, ensuring a voyage marked by innovation and safety.\nUltimate Comfort: Immerse yourself in luxury with air conditioning providing a perfect onboard climate. A generator ensures a continuous power supply, enhancing your comfort on every leg of the journey.\n• Effortless Sailing: Experience the ease of electric winches, elevating your sailing adventure with minimal effort. Maneuvering becomes a breeze, allowing you to focus on the joy of the voyage.\n• Revolutionary Furling Mainsail: “Lella Belle” features a cutting-edge furling mainsail, adding a touch of innovation to your sailing experience. Effortlessly adjust your sail area, adapting to changing winds with ease.\nYour Nautical Sanctuary Awaits:\n\n“Lella Belle” invites you to embrace the freedom of the open sea. Whether you’re an experienced sailor or a novice adventurer, this vessel promises a journey that transcends expectations. Feel the gentle sway of the waves, the whisper of the wind, and the serenity of endless horizons aboard your own floating sanctuary.\n\nSecure Your Sailing Experience:\n\nReady to make “Lella Belle” your nautical home? Contact us now to secure your place aboard this vessel of distinction. Whether you seek a solo sojourn, a romantic escape, or a family adventure, “Lella Belle” ensures an unforgettable maritime experience in 2024 and beyond.","blueprint":{"name":"LELLA BELLE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::496e45b0-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::5023c2a0-412d-11f0-add3-5fbc684733cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::50306cd0-412d-11f0-add3-5fbc684733cb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::498b4390-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::498c5500-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::4a238bf0-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::4a184150-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::906d12d0-4128-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::498f6240-412e-11f0-b9c5-03310a2e9fb4/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Beneteau","model":"Oceanis 46.1","maxCrew":1,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::203e5c80-1114-11ee-9252-8dfbe7b06027","name":"Alimos Marina","coordinates":{"latitude":37.9143789425662,"longitude":23.70482919549218},"country":"Greece"},"builtYear":2024,"fuelCapacity":200,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Double Cabins","value":"4"},{"label":"Bunk Cabin","value":"1"}],"cabins":5,"bathrooms":3,"length":13.65,"beam":4.5,"draft":2,"hullType":"Monohull","engines":"Yanmar 80HP","amenities":[{"label":"Air Condition"},{"label":"Generator "},{"label":"Fans In Saloon & Cabins"},{"label":"220V sockets "},{"label":"Bow Thruster"},{"label":"Cockpit Cushions"},{"label":"USB Sockets Saloon & Cabins"},{"label":" Electric Toilets"},{"labe